author: Xbox
description:
Travelers! Let’s dive deep into the twisted time-travel story of Cronos: The New Dawn in our new developer diary! Join our Lead Writer, Grzegorz Like, and Producer, Klaudia Sewera, as they explore the core narrative themes behind our vision of survival horror. 

The game will arrive on September 5 to Xbox Series X|S and PC.
